                     <interp inst="t17840526-66-person611" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                  </persName>
            , a mariner on board a certain other vessel called the Scorpion, supposing he was intitled to certain wages, in order to receive the same.</p>
               <p>
            
                  <persName id="t17840526-66-person612">
                  JAMES
                   SLADE
