               <p>PRISONER's DEFENCE.</p>
               <p>I was distressed, was the reason of my having done so, I had wages due, I beg my life.</p>
               <p>Court to Scott. What sort of a man was the prisoner? - A very good man indeed, I never knew a better.</p>
